{"about_the_game":"Starting today, you are admitted to Whimel Magic Academy! <i>Whimel Academy</i> is a famous magic school where a variety of subjects are offered to the students. You will also meet fellow students, with whom you can develop friendships and potentially romance. Your only goal is to have a fulfilling student life and fruitful education during your six years here. You'll need to put aside time to earn some extra pocket money, all while balancing your classes, hobbies, and friendships. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/dorm.gif?t=1738604765\" /><br><br>\ud83c\udf31 Whimel Academy is a cozy, slow-paced time management game where the player decide what to do from day to day, in addition the players can choose to romance one of several in-game characters. Whimel Academy aims to be a wholesome experience where the players can immerse themselves in a low-stake fantasy world and role-play as an ordinary student in a magic school.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/header_time_management.png?t=1738604765\" /><br>You need to decide where and how to spend your limited time among activities such as taking classes and spending time with your friends, and also pay attention to your health and finance. <br>\u2728 Take classes.<br>\u2728 Practice magic outside class.<br>\u2728 Take part-time jobs to earn money and skill.<br>\u2728 Shop for magical supplies.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/classroom.gif?t=1738604765\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/header_relationships.png?t=1738604765\" /><br>You can befriend (or romance) a variety of characters of different genders and personality. There won't be any life-or-death plot line, but you can really get to know each one of them through various conversations and interactions.<br><br>\u2728 Male, Female and gender-nonbinary characters.<br>\u2728 Unique personalities and deep narratives.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/lumi_dialogue.gif?t=1738604765\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/header_low_fantasy.png?t=1738604765\" /><br>Whimel aims to create a wholesome fantasy world where you can feel relaxed and as if coming to home through the low-stake gameplay, cozy atmosphere and detailed slice-of-life worldbuilding. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/map.gif?t=1738604765\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/header_endings.png?t=1738604765\" /><br>You can specialize in different tracks of magic throughout the game. Different combinations of stats would grant you one of the 30+ endings when you graduate.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/big_ui.gif?t=1738604765\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Received Letter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2377250/d843a69ea6dc034c44af3cc011efd483a1a4c913.jpg"},{"name":"Ending","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2377250/e94dee55a7672675d47b1458b3894f1b9011a921.jpg"},{"name":"Scholarship","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2377250/61fd1a8c0996396df0db910907f462f0c42340eb.jpg"},{"name":"Nom Nom","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2377250/7e49e1dadf4ee7d81151f65bc6cd7d2e3d3af34b.jpg"},{"name":"Decoration","path":